        <title>Lambda và Stream trong Java 8: Hướng dẫn nhanh</title>
        <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/lambda-va-stream-trong-java-8-huong-dan-nhanh/</link>
        <pubDate>Thu, 25 Dec 2025 10:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
        
        <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/lambda-va-stream-trong-java-8-huong-dan-nhanh/</guid>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;Trong Java 8, &lt;code&gt;lambda&lt;/code&gt; và &lt;code&gt;Stream API&lt;/code&gt; giúp viết mã ngắn gọn, dễ đọc và theo phong cách lập trình hàm.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lambda: Biểu thức hàm gọn nhẹ thay cho class ẩn danh.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stream: Xử lý tập dữ liệu theo pipeline (map, filter, reduce).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ví dụ đơn giản với &lt;code&gt;lambda&lt;/code&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-java&#34; data-lang=&#34;java&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;List&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;String&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; names &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; List.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;of&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;An&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;Bình&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;Chi&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;names.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;forEach&lt;/span&gt;(n &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;-&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; System.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;out&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;println&lt;/span&gt;(n));
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Ví dụ &lt;code&gt;Stream&lt;/code&gt; lọc và chuyển đổi:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-java&#34; data-lang=&#34;java&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;List&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;Integer&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; numbers &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; List.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;of&lt;/span&gt;(1,2,3,4,5);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;List&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;Integer&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; evenSquares &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; numbers.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;stream&lt;/span&gt;()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    .&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;filter&lt;/span&gt;(n &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;-&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; n &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;%&lt;/span&gt; 2 &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;==&lt;/span&gt; 0)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    .&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;map&lt;/span&gt;(n &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;-&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; n &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; n)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    .&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;toList&lt;/span&gt;();
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Một pipeline phổ biến:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Nguồn dữ liệu: &lt;code&gt;collection.stream()&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Trung gian: &lt;code&gt;filter&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;map&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;sorted&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Tổng hợp: &lt;code&gt;collect&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;reduce&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;count&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Lưu ý hiệu năng: &lt;code&gt;stream()&lt;/code&gt; là lazy, chỉ thực thi khi gặp operation tổng hợp. Dùng &lt;code&gt;parallelStream()&lt;/code&gt; cho danh sách lớn nhưng cần đo đạc trước.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Khi nào dùng:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Duyệt danh sách + chuyển đổi dữ liệu.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Thay thế vòng lặp lồng nhau bằng pipeline rõ ràng.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Kết luận: Lambda + Stream giúp code Java hiện đại, súc tích và an toàn hơn.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
